<div class="fl-module fl-module-heading fl-node-5cf797b17a771 title" data-node="5cf797b17a771">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<h2 class="fl-heading">
		<span class="fl-heading-text">19th-20th Century Fine Western Art & Collectibles</span>
	</h2>
	</div>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
	</div>

<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-5cf79d8e727d9" data-node="5cf79d8e727d9">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-5cf79d8e72957" data-node="5cf79d8e72957">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content">
	<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-5cf79d8e7276a small-body" data-node="5cf79d8e7276a">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p>The Bozeman Trail Gallery is located in Sheridan, Wyoming along the eastern slopes of the Bighorn Mountains. Offering an assortment of some of the finest American West artwork in the region, the gallery specializes in 19th and 20th century western art, American Indian beadwork, Navajo rugs and blankets, and cowboy collectibles.</p>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-5cf7a0f1afdce fl-visible-desktop" data-node="5cf7a0f1afdce">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-photo fl-photo-align-center" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
